title: Thai Green Curry Variation 1
method: Fry curry paste in a little oil for 1–2 minutes until fragrant.
Add coconut milk and bring to a gentle simmer.
Add chicken and cook for 15 minutes until nearly cooked.
Add vegetables, fish sauce, and sugar; simmer for 10 more minutes.
Serve with jasmine rice and garnish with basil leaves.
hydrationTip: Pair with water or iced green tea to balance the spices.
